1. *Bolesni* ljudi moraju leći u krevet. (Sick people must lie in bed.)
2. Moramo posjetiti *bolesnu* prijateljicu u bolnici. (We need to visit our *sick* friend in the hospital.)
3. *Bolesnim* pacijentima treba pružiti adekvatnu njegu. (Proper care should be provided to *sick* patients.)
4. Naša mačka izgleda *bolesno*, moramo je odvesti veterinaru. (Our cat looks *sick*, we need to take her to the vet.)
5. Ljubav prema novcu može biti *bolesna* opsesija. (Love for money can be a *sick* obsession.)
6. U ovom trenutku društvo se suočava sa *bolesnim* pojavama kriminala. (At this moment, society is facing *sick* criminal activities.)
7. Njen pogled bio je *bolesno* crn. (Her look was *sickly* dark.)
8. U ovoj sobi vlada *bolesna* tišina. (A *sickening* silence prevails in this room.)
9. Nakon operacije osjećao se *bolesno* i vrtjelo mu se u glavi. (After the surgery, he felt *sick* and dizzy.)
10. Taj plan je *bolesno* glup. (That plan is *insanely* stupid.)